162 PHORMIO.

Ac‘r IV. SCENE 6. [V. 6.]

Geta suddenly issues from the house of Demipho in great excitement. By some adroit eavesdropping he has learnt the secret about Chremes’ Lemnian daughter and her identity with Phanium. All this he relates to Phormio and Phaedria.
